# EDUNEXUS ENTERPRISE BACKEND

## PHASE 1.4 – SHARED CORE FRAMEWORK

You are continuing the EduNexus Enterprise Backend.

**Phase 1.1 (Project Bootstrap), Phase 1.2 (Database Foundation), and Phase 1.3 (Enterprise Infrastructure Services) are complete.**

Do NOT recreate the project.

Do NOT regenerate existing files unless integration requires it.

Generate only **production-ready source code files**.

Do NOT generate documentation.

Do NOT generate planning documents.

Do NOT generate placeholder implementations.

Every generated file must compile successfully.

---

# TECHNOLOGY STACK

* NestJS
* TypeScript
* Prisma ORM
* PostgreSQL
* Redis
* RabbitMQ
* Docker

Continue using the existing enterprise architecture.

---

# OBJECTIVE

Build the **Shared Core Framework** that every future EduNexus module depends on.

This phase creates reusable enterprise components to eliminate duplicated code across all modules.

**Do NOT generate Authentication, Users, Roles, Permissions, or business modules.**

---

