* UUID Primary Keys
* created_at
* updated_at
* deleted_at (Soft Delete)
* created_by
* updated_by
* deleted_by
* version (Optimistic Locking)
* tenant_id
* school_group_id
* school_id
* campus_id

These become mandatory for future entities.

